#. <p> 354--360
#: release-notes.sgml:354
msgid ""
"Between releases 2.2 (`potato') and 3.0 (`woody'), a number of packages have "
"been split into two or more packages. The reason for these splits, in "
"general, is that the original package provided a diverse set of "
"functionalities, and that few, if any, users used all of these components."
